This paper is about improving the efficiency of neural machine translation (NMT) decoding on CPUs. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which includes papers on natural language processing and machine translation. The paper also proposes a new network architecture, which falls under the category of deep learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The techniques used to speed up the decoder involve optimizing the search algorithm, which could fall under the category of optimization (cs.NE). Finally, the paper uses the WMT English-French NewsTest2014 dataset, which involves image captioning and object recognition, falling under the category of computer vision (cs.CV).
